                        <note n="5" xml:id="note-t-5">
                            

<p>From 2 January to 9 February 1890, <rs xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" type="person" ref="bio.xml#_407">Willemien</rs> stayed with Theo and <rs xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" type="person" ref="bio.xml#_416">Jo</rs> in order to help out during the last weeks of Jo’s pregnancy and during her confinement.</p>
                        </note>
                        
                    
